TEAMS Bahrain


Another division of BASREC, Technical Engineering and Marketing Services (TEAMS-Bahrain) is an electrical engineering company specializing in the manufacture, modification and maintenance of switchboards, motor control centers and control panels. It has a dedicated team, many of whom have more than 25 years of experience in the switchgear and control panel industry, and are well-equipped to tackle technical challenges and meet critical shut down periods.
Associated with many of the leading, reputed electrical and mechanical engineering product brand names in the industry, TEAMS-Bahrain has for many years catered to the needs of Bahrain’s industries with various specialized products, and hopes to prove its competency in the future.






 


















 



